title: and Scheana Shay
description:
Scheana Shay spills the tea on #PumpRules and BF Brock Davies! She answers all the hard-hitting questions about their first meet, first date, whether she gave it up on that first date, how he managed to surprise her with a trip to Bali, and if Brock will ever be on “Vanderpump Rules”! She’s also dishing on Brett Caprioni, the making of her music video, “One More Time,” and her new YouTube Channel.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
